{"tid":300443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「老公」床上攬女吳若希投訴冇碇瞓","createTime":"2017-06-28T02:01:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T02:17:36.000Z","uid":48800,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d250182e49fa873cd5bd42a63c36261c21556b1f","tid":300443,"uid":48800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T02:01:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/28/095952_dc35cee1820635bbbf778ff36f3eb8a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F28%2F095952_dc35cee1820635bbbf778ff36f3eb8a5.jpg&h=6988d538&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【東方日報專訊】歌手吳若希（Jinny）前晚在社交網上載「老公」Alex於床上抱着寶貝女Giselle的溫馨相，地位被搶的Jinny酸溜溜寫下：「又唔使咁Sweet嘅。」隨即投訴：「有沒有人打算留個位置給我？」由於Giselle面珠脹卜卜非常可愛，不少網民留言「想啜啖佢」。<br />\n<br />\nJinny接受電話訪問時稱，囡囡現時主要飲人奶及奶粉：「佢係偏大食，平均三個鐘食一餐，人奶兩個鐘左右就肚餓。」並指兩個多月大的Giselle已戒夜奶：「夜晚食完十二點鐘嗰餐就瞓到朝早六、七點再食。（人奶夠佢食？）正常，唔係好多，夠佢一餐分量。朝早就人奶，夜晚就飲奶粉，都幾肥肥白白。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/%E8%80%81%E5%85%AC-%E5%BA%8A%E4%B8%8A%E6%94%AC%E5%A5%B3%E5%90%B3%E8%8B%A5%E5%B8%8C%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4%E5%86%87%E7%A2%87%E7%9E%93-222017084.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.celebrity.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%2585%25AC-%25E5%25BA%258A%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%2594%25AC%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%2590%25B3%25E8%258B%25A5%25E5%25B8%258C%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E5%2586%2587%25E7%25A2%2587%25E7%259E%2593-222017084.html&d=AWFfUEWSyAy1hQVEKdBgyJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=45639646\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/%E8%80%81%E5%85%AC-%E5%BA%8A%E4%B8%8A%E6%94%AC%E5%A5%B3%E5%90%B3%E8%8B%A5%E5%B8%8C%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4%E5%86%87%E7%A2%87%E7%9E%93-222017084.html</a><br />\n<br />\n留名睇改圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"362a9999c848488094900443b6d1b736b004f291","tid":300443,"uid":72454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T02:02:57.000Z","msg":"遺傳到喎 大